groceries.name: Alphonso Mangoes
groceries.description: Savor the sweetness of Alphonso Mangoes, known as the 'King of Mangoes.' Grown in the sunny orchards of Ratnagiri, Maharashtra, these mangoes are famous for their rich taste and juicy pulp.

groceries.name: Basmati Rice
groceries.description: Experience the aroma and long-grain perfection of Basmati Rice, grown in the fertile fields of Punjab. This premium rice variety is a staple in Indian households and complements a wide range of dishes.

groceries.name: Assam Black Tea
groceries.description: Indulge in the robust flavor of Assam Black Tea, harvested from the lush tea gardens of Assam. This strong and malty tea is perfect for morning refreshment or a delightful afternoon cuppa.

groceries.name: Turmeric Powder
groceries.description: Add a burst of color and earthy flavor to your dishes with Turmeric Powder, sourced from the spice-rich lands of Kerala. This golden spice is a staple in Indian cooking and offers numerous health benefits.

groceries.name: Rajma (Kidney Beans)
groceries.description: Enjoy the hearty taste of Rajma (Kidney Beans), a popular North Indian delicacy. Cultivated in the mountains of Himachal Pradesh, Rajma is a protein-rich addition to your meals.

groceries.name: Pure Ghee
groceries.description: Indulge in the rich flavor of Pure Ghee, handcrafted in the traditional way in the heartland of Uttar Pradesh. This clarified butter adds a delightful taste to Indian sweets and savory dishes.

groceries.name: Spicy Masala Mix
groceries.description: Add a burst of flavor to your dishes with the Spicy Masala Mix from Kerala. This exotic blend of spices is perfect for enhancing the taste of curries, biryanis, and other Indian delicacies.

groceries.name: Assorted Indian Sweets Box
groceries.description: Indulge in the rich and sweet taste of India with the Assorted Indian Sweets Box by SweetDelights. This delightful box includes a variety of traditional Indian sweets that are perfect for celebrations.

groceries.name: Organic Basmati Rice
groceries.description: Embrace healthy eating with the Organic Basmati Rice from Himalayan Farms. Grown without harmful chemicals, this aromatic rice is ideal for making wholesome and delicious meals.

groceries.name: Handpicked Darjeeling Tea
groceries.description: Savor the exquisite flavor of Handpicked Darjeeling Tea, plucked from the tea gardens of Darjeeling. This premium tea offers a delicate and refreshing taste that tea connoisseurs will appreciate.

groceries.name: Fresh Organic Vegetables Basket
groceries.description: Fuel your body with nutrition from the Fresh Organic Vegetables Basket by OrganicHarvest. Packed with a variety of seasonal veggies, it ensures a healthy and balanced diet for you and your family.

groceries.name: Premium Filter Coffee Powder
groceries.description: Awaken your senses with the rich aroma of Premium Filter Coffee Powder from Karnataka. Made from the finest coffee beans, it brews a perfect cup of traditional South Indian filter coffee.
